"Well, Wei, just give the boy three more days. If he doesn't solve it, we'll solve it for him. What do you say?" The secretary hurriedly persuades way.



"You just spoil him."



The village chief dismissed the secretary and left in anger.



"Oh, what can I say to you, boy? Remember, three days, only three days, after three days do not deal with, I will help you deal with!"



The secretary sighed and left.
